    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Assurance level is designated High based on the refined mesh convergence study (GCI < 4%), dual-QoI validation coverage, and quantitative output comparison within expanded uncertainty bands at all five operating points. The assessment team concludes the CFD model provides sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission decision that the device meets the RH < 1 hemolysis criterion relative to the predicate device.",
